{"tid":929012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"社群媒體賣裸露照月入17萬 妙齡女：是門好生意","createTime":"2018-12-05T09:33:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T09:45:10.000Z","uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"84e026ceda75d243a3baecf057c7e192433d88ea","tid":929012,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T09:33:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/12/04/99/5619667.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F12%2F04%2F99%2F5619667.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=69e887e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n26歲的朱迪（Jodie Carnall）靠在社群媒體Snapchat販賣色情影像給訂戶，月入5800美元。&nbsp;<br />\n全球有30.3億社群媒體活躍使用者，社群媒體深植人類生活，如今又有新的功用：拍攝色情照賺錢。一名26歲英國女性朱迪（Jodie Carnall）就靠在社群媒體Snapchat販賣色情影像給訂戶，月入5800美元（約新台幣17萬8000元）。<br />\n據BBC中文網報導，26歲的朱迪原從事辦公室類型的工作，但工作條件不好，因此決定開發新的賺錢手段。她2016年開始在Snapchat上以每月25美元（約新台幣770元）到250美元（約新台幣7700元）訂閱費，販賣自己的裸露照片和影音給訂閱者，偶爾也針對不同需求拍客製化影片。<br />\n朱迪稱自己是「Snapchat高级女郎」，她現在有40個訂閱者且收入是從前的4倍，她認為這門好生意可以讓她經濟更自由。朱迪說：「這跟歌手唱歌或藝術家賣畫一樣，我是在賣自己的影像和照片。」<br />\n但這份工作也給朱迪帶來許多困擾，她幾乎每小時都收到批評或騷擾的訊息，而約會對象一知道她的職業便退避三舍。「我好幾個月沒交男朋友了&hellip;&hellip;有時我會哭，因為我得不到任何善意的關注。」朱迪也可能遭遇「色情報復」，因為訂閱者可能散布這些內容，而來勒索她。<br />\n英國律師表示，在英國出售裸露視頻並不違法，除非客戶未滿18或是內容太過露骨。而Snapchat則回應，他們規定禁止發布色情內容，一旦發現就會刪除，不過朱迪的生意從2016年開始從未間斷。而在台灣網路販賣自拍裸露照片及影片，則可能觸犯刑法第二百三十四條第一項之「公然猥褻罪」，及刑法第二百三十五條第一項之「散佈猥褻物品罪」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/12/04/99/5619619.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F12%2F04%2F99%2F5619619.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=33ca7ffe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n26歲英國女性朱迪（Jodie Carnall）靠在社群媒體Snapchat販賣色情影像給訂戶，月入5800美元。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/12/04/99/5619618.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F12%2F04%2F99%2F5619618.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=fc546836&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱迪稱自己是「Snapchat高级女郎」，她認為這門好生意讓她經濟更自由。&nbsp;<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6810/3518440?from=udn-catehotnews_ch2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6810%2F3518440%3Ffrom%3Dudn-catehotnews_ch2&d=9DBRqKeZ%2Fbmcg3Dx4ivvIviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=781604f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6810/3518440?from=udn-catehotnews_ch2</a>"},{"pid":"31864699c0ed3161c2b93c4c069f39937c5173f2","tid":929012,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T09:34:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce5b1a9aa14f245522f6fa99c307fbb3dc4c1089","tid":929012,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T09:34:43.000Z","msg":"同妓女一樣"},{"pid":"235e1d64ae47ef9ee5c3e7a608792bb58b7f28a6","tid":929012,"uid":77569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T09:34:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"037b4926c067299571ceb1a8eeccaa50e817388a","tid":929012,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"235e1d64ae47ef9ee5c3e7a608792bb58b7f28a6","tid":929012,"uid":77569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T09:34:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T09:38:03.000Z","msg":"入黎正想講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023356122f67ca68e3876332a5ab508d465772c9","tid":929012,"uid":30821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T09:38:16.000Z","msg":"女性身體自主<img src=\